---
title: Homestyle Chive and Cheddar Biscuits Serves 2 | Great on their own or a flavourful addition to any meal
description: Better than grandma's biscuits? We'd say so! These DIY cheesy biscuits are packed full of savoury chives and sharp cheddar cheese!
